description:
On this weeks edition of WHAT'S BURNIN', Matt and Stephen break down the Nets impressive 5-0 west coast trip and the Mavs red-hot offense. Plus, they react to Anthony Edwards crazy dunk vs. the Cavs and talk Toronto turning around their season. Also, the boys answer fan questions and more.
